body { margin: 0; font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 200; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
h1, h2 { color: #22465e; font-weight: 200; }
div.titleCard h1, div.titleCard h2 { padding: 0; }
div.titleCard h1 { margin: 12px 12px 2px 12px; font-size: 30px; }
div.titleCard h2 { margin: 2px 12px 24px 12px; font-size: 18px; }
div.titleCard img { position: absolute; top: 14px; right: 14px; width: 72px; height: 72px; }
ul#tabs { width: 97%; list-style-type: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
ul#tabs li { width: 25%; float: left; background-position: 14px 12px; height: 48px; }
ul#tabs li a { color: #58676d; font-size: 11px; height: 27px; text-decoration: none; display: block; border-bottom: 3px solid #d0d8d8; margin: 12px 0 12px 12px; padding: 12px 0 0 42px; }
ul#tabs li a.selected { color: #53bbd4; border-bottom: 3px solid #53bbd4; }
div.tabContent { color: #918e8b; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; padding: 16px; margin-top: 50px; background-color: #fff; }
div.tabContent h2:first-child { margin-top: 48px; }
div.tabContent h2 { color: #58676d; margin-top: 46px; }
div.tabContent.hide { display: none; }
div.tabContent ul, div.tabContent ol { padding-left: 1.2em; }
div.twoCols:first-child { margin-right: 6%; }
div.twoCols { width: 47%; float: left; }
table { border-collapse: collapse; color: #918e8b; }
table, th, td { border: 1px solid gray; }
th, td { text-align: left; font-size: 100%; padding: 2px 12px 2px 6px; }
#img1 { background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 34px 32px; background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }
a#img1.selected { background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }
#img2 { background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 23px 33px; background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }
a#img2.selected { background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }
#img3 { background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 29px 33px; background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }
a#img3.selected { background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }
#img4 { background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 29px 33px; background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }
a#img4.selected { background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,); }

@media (max-width: 640px) {
   div.titleCard h1 { font-size: 21px; }
   div.titleCard h2 { font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
   div.titleCard img { position: absolute; top: 14px; right: 14px; width: 44px; height: 44px; }
   ul#tabs li { text-align: center; }

   #img1, #img2, #img3, #img4 { background-position: 50% 16px; }

   ul#tabs li a { font-size: 10px; margin: 0; padding: 42px 0 0 0; height: 48px; width: 100%; border-bottom: none; }



   ul#tabs li a.selected { border-bottom: none; }
   #img1 { width: 25px; height: 24px; background-size: 25px 24px; }
   #img2 { width: 17px; height: 24px; background-size: 17px 24px; }
   #img3 { width: 22px; height: 24px; background-size: 22px 24px; }
   #img4 { width: 21px; height: 24px; background-size: 21px 24px; }
   div.tabContent { color: #22465e; font-size: 75%; line-height: 1.4em; }
   div.tabContent h2:first-child { margin-top: 10px; }
   div.tabContent h2 { color: #58676d; margin-top: 42px; }
   div.twoCols { width: 100%; margin-right: 0; }
   div.twoCols:last-child { margin-top: 42px; }
   table { color: #22465e; }
}
